snippet.title: Persona Q2: New Cinema Labyrinth | Phantom Thieves Trailer
snippet.description:
https://atlus.com/personaq2/

While Joker may win the trophy for Best Protagonist, the award for Best Supporting Cast goes to the Phantom Thieves from Persona 5, who will help Joker fight the evil lurking in Persona Q2: New Cinema Labyrinth!

Pre-order today: https://amzn.to/2WCXUZg
